                    Watch them made while you wait for yours! They also serve Hawaiian Shaved Ice, their Famous Sausage Subs, and Cheese Steaks, too! Your taste buds will water every time you pass by!
                    The Amusement Center is full of games for the whole family – old favorites like Skee Ball and Wheel Deal plus the latest 
                    high-tech, non-violent Video and Driving Games for all ages. Select your prizes at the Redemption Counter which has the most varied assortment
                    you’ve ever seen. Not enough points yet? Don’t Worry. Your points NEVER expire at Fannie Farkle’s Family Fun Parlor!
                </p>
